I"r<ol>
  <li>Install firmware:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>wget http://jusst.de/manu/fw/AFA/dvb-usb-af9015.fw_a-link
<span class="nb">sudo mv </span>dvb-usb-af9015.fw_a-link /lib/firmware/dvb-usb-af9015.fw
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Install <code class="highlighter-rouge">w_scan</code>:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>wget http://wirbel.htpc-forum.de/w_scan/w_scan-20130331.tar.bz2
<span class="nb">tar </span>xvf w_scan-20130331.tar.bz2
<span class="nb">cd </span>w_scan-20130331
./configure
make <span class="o">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class="nb">sudo </span>make <span class="nb">install</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Scan channels:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>w_scan <span class="nt">-ft</span> <span class="nt">-c</span> BE <span class="nt">-X</span> <span class="nt">-R</span> N <span class="nt">-O</span> N <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> ~/.mplayer/channels.conf
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Play with <code class="highlighter-rouge">mplayer</code>:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>mplayer dvb://
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

